snippet.title: Cyber Knight
snippet.description:
When I am found to be deceased and unable to continue the Minesweeper Let's Play series, anyone else is allowed to continue the series on their own channel so long as they follow the proper format of the series. 

- Each episode must have the title "Let's Play Minesweeper - Episode (N of previous episode + 1)" regardless of whether the English language and modern counting system have changed or gone extinct. 
- Each episode must be roughly ten minutes in length. 
- Each episode must be a 2-dimensional recording of the game Minesweeper. No live events, holographic recordings, etc.
- This exact text must be copied and pasted on one's about page (or equivalent on another website) if they take up the mantle.
- One video shall be uploaded per day (24 hours). If you miss a day, keep a log of missed episodes and upload multiple later.
- The series is not allowed to end.
